How do I install VirtualBox Guest Additions on Linux Mint

- Devices > Insert Guest Additions CD image
- cancel
- Double click on the CD icon on your desktop. It should be labeled VBOXADDITIONS_X.X.X_YYYYY, where X and Y are numbers.
- Open in Terminal
- "sudo apt-get purge virtualbox*"
- pass
- "clear"
- "sudo bash ./VBoxLinuxAdditions.run"
- "exit"
- eject CD
- shut down system
- In VirtualBox 
- Setting/Display
- Video memory + Enable 3D Acceleration
- verify "dmesg | egrep -i 'virtualbox|vbox'"
- .... vboxguest ...
